# Repo-wide shellcheck config. The CI lint job gates at -S style (every
# severity level); per-finding opt-outs carry an inline rationale at the site.
#
# SC2292 (prefer [[ ]] over [ ]): disabled repo-wide. The codebase uses [ ]
# throughout (~557 sites); a mechanical conversion is not semantics-preserving
# ([[ ]] treats an unquoted RHS of = / != as a glob PATTERN, and changes
# empty/word-split behaviour), so the rewrite risk vastly outweighs the
# stylistic gain on a protocol whose conditionals are individually reasoned
# about.
disable=SC2292
